 all,::One      `-----'        ring::to
   ::find:::                  them,:One
    Ring:::::to            bring::them
      all::and::in:the:darkness:bind
        them:In:the:Land:of:Mordor
           where:::the::Shadows
                :::lie.:::

 Envoyer par email	
.--------------------------------+---------------------------+----------------------------.
: One Ring to rule them all,     | Ash nazg durbatulk,      | Ein Ring, sie zu knechten, :
: One Ring to find them,         | Ash nazg gimbatul,        | sie alle zu finden,        :
: One Ring to bring them all,    | Ash nazg thrakatulk,     | Ins Dunkel zu treiben      :
: and in the darkness bind them. | Agh burzum-ishi krimpatul | und ewig zu binden         :
'--------------------------------+---------------------------+----------------------------'
